# Implementation Plan - Sakakibara Tax Website First View

## Goal
Create a professional, responsive "First View" for Sakakibara Tax Accountant Office (榊原税理士事務所) referencing Japanese corporate design standards.

## Design Specs
- **Colors**:
    - Deep Navy: `#1F2A44` (Sub/Backgrounds)
    - Gold: `#BDAA4B` (Accents/Buttons)
    - Warm Gray: `#F4F4F2` (Base/Text)
- **Typography**:
    - Headings: `Noto Serif JP` (Mincho) for trust/tradition.
    - Body: `Noto Sans JP` (Gothic) for readability.
- **Layout**:
    - Hero Section: Full viewport height.
    - Text: Vertical orientation (Tategaki) for the main message.
    - Navigation: Minimalist, top or hamburger menu (depending on mobile).

